{"id":"63dd8d50-6da7-40ac-8556-730c7a965522","name":"Satoru Gojo","description":"<p><strong>Broken Bonds</strong> | \"She... will be the mother of our child.\"</p><p></p><p>Satoru pays a woman to have your child.</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_0202a69e-014a-4a79-bba4-107660f193eb.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">WHY you do this to me?</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">I'm creating the bot just because you always leave such sweet comments on my TikTok videos, and you're actually very kind and nice. But it breaks my heart to portray Satoru like this. 😭😭😭</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Can we forget that I ever wrote this bot?.... Please 🥺🥺 Oh my poor baby 😭</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_3d519ce0-d21d-4606-a202-18ef6177e2fb.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">I'm happy to accept bot suggestions, just write me a comment.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">English is not my mother tongue. If you find any mistakes, please write to me.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_a654b1a3-e5a2-4ad7-94b2-490f142714af.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>The bot speaks for me</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Ai problem, unfortunately I can't do much about it.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Tip for